Carl Froch was due to fight Julio Cesar Chavez Jnr in Las Vegas this month . 
  The WBA super-middleweight champion was forced to withdraw with a shoulder injury . 
  Chavez faces Andrzej Fonfara on Saturday night but is open to facing Froch . 
  Froch is keen to fight in the US and would be open to travelling to Las Vegas . 
 